tbrFsCEUuq2S5lraOln4nQ
The food was really good. Ordered the Pad Thai, the Panang Curry, and some veggie rolls. Everything was very tasty. The Panang Curry is some of the best of I've ever had. Really rich, creamy, and very tasty. The spice scale is a little misleading. I would have ordered one number higher if I had known that. None the less, it is still really good food. The service here is good, quick, and friendly as well. The location is really convenient if you are attending any events downtown. I highly recommend this place!

